{"TopicId":172244,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[KSP 1.12.x] Keep It Straight - Camera Persistent Mode (1.4.0) - 2021-11-03","CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-14T09:03:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-14T09:03:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162682-realgecko/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022162682\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162682-realgecko/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@RealGecko\u003C/a\u003E stopped supporting this mod and turned this over to me. Original thread is here: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/143175-ksp-131-keep-it-straight-camera-persistent-mode-103-2017-10-11/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/143175-ksp-131-keep-it-straight-camera-persistent-mode-103-2017-10-11/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen I\u0027m on a low orbit I prefer FREE camera mode, cause body I\u0027m \u0022falling to\u0022 has to be \u0022below\u0022 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever KSP keeps switching camera mode to AUTO every time something happens: switched to far away vessel, ended docking etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo here is Keep It Straight - mod that saves camera mode between scene changes and restores it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EPhotorealistic pictures from high orbit made by RealGecko:\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022l2TvNlv.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022575\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022http://imgur.com/l2TvNlv.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022LKynjPl.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022575\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022http://imgur.com/LKynjPl.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo more, no less \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ESource: \u003C/strong\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/jarosm/KSP-KeepItStraight\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/jarosm/KSP-KeepItStraight\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EDownload:\u003C/strong\u003E \u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/824/Keep%20It%20Straight\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://spacedock.info/mod/824/Keep%20It%20Straight\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ELicense: \u003C/strong\u003EGPL-3.0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EChangelog:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVersion 1.4.0\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nKSP 1.12\u002B compatibility\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVersion 1.3.0\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nKSP 1.11\u002B compatibility\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVersion 1.2.0\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nKSP 1.10\u002B compatibility\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVersion 1.1.0\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nKSP 1.8\u002B compatibility\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVersion 1.0.7\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nRecompile for KSP 1.7.1\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVersion 1.0.6\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nRecompile for KSP 1.7\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVersion 1.0.5\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nRecompile for KSP 1.5\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVersion 1.0.4\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nRecompile for KSP 1.4.1\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVersion 1.0.3\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nRecompile for KSP 1.3.1\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVersion 1.0.2\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nRecompile for KSP 1.3.0\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EVersion 1.0.1\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nCamera mode is not reset to AUTO after docking is complete\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-11-03T17:32:33Z\u0022 title=\u002211/03/2021 05:32  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 3, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by maja\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"leatherneck6017","CreatedById":178617,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-03-14T15:15:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for the update. I used this a lot in my 1.3 game, will be nice to have it again in 1.4.1.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-19T08:05:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENew release for KSP 1.5 is live!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo changes in this little piece of gem\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-10-19T12:27:00Z\u0022 title=\u002210/19/2018 12:27  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 19, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by maja\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaverickSawyer","CreatedById":11952,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-19T18:58:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anyone else have an issue with this not registering a change when docking to a space station? I.E., I dock to the station while in Free mode, and the station was in Free mode just before docking, but after docking, I\u0027m in Auto.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-10-19T19:09:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223471381\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172244\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221539975535\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002211952\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaverickSawyer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 10/19/2018 at 8:58 PM, MaverickSawyer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes anyone else have an issue with this not registering a change when docking to a space station? I.E., I dock to the station while in Free mode, and the station was in Free mode just before docking, but after docking, I\u0027m in Auto.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan you create an issue on the github? I test it when I have a litlle bit of time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: Tested. It\u0027s working as expected. Camera is maintained in selected mode after dock/undock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-06-03T17:10:55Z\u0022 title=\u002206/03/2019 05:10  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EJune 3, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by maja\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-04-28T18:19:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENew release for KSP 1.7 is live!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-03T17:09:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENew release for KSP 1.7.1 is live!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-20T11:34:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENew release for KSP 1.8 is live!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"leatherneck6017","CreatedById":178617,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-10-20T13:45:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223690910\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172244\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221571571245\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022168379\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022maja\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, maja said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENew release for KSP 1.8 is live!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is such a must have mod for me. Thanks for taking over and maintaining it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-07-20T17:53:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ENew release for KSP 1.10 is live!\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aerodinamic Potatoe","CreatedById":201241,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-04T02:49:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVERYY THAANKS I NEEDED THIS \u0026lt;3\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ocewatt","CreatedById":207781,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-11-03T11:02:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have to express my appreciation for this mod, thank you for making something that should be a stock feature!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-07T14:51:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:18px;\u0022\u003ENew release for KSP 1.11.1\u00A0is live!\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-02-16T20:38:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you for keeping this going! Constantly cycling through to free mode was indeed quite annoying\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-08T18:55:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThis mod is no longer needed in the KSP 1.12.x\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jefferyharrell","CreatedById":27205,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-22T17:17:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224001543\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172244\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221625770547\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022168379\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022maja\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/8/2021 at 11:55 AM, maja said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EThis mod is no longer needed in the KSP 1.12.x\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not entirely sure I agree. This mod keeps my camera from switching from Free mode to Orbital mode automatically during ascents.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-25T09:20:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224023046\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172244\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629652639\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227205\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022jefferyharrell\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 8/22/2021 at 7:17 PM, jefferyharrell said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not entirely sure I agree. This mod keeps my camera from switching from Free mode to Orbital mode automatically during ascents.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you for mentioning it. I will recompile it, because I didn\u0027t catch this problem.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jefferyharrell","CreatedById":27205,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-25T16:45:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224024025\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022172244\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221629883207\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022168379\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022maja\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, maja said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you for mentioning it. I will recompile it, because I didn\u0027t catch this problem.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLet me clarify: Without this mod, the camera automatically switches from Free to Orbital mode when periapsis hits a certain whatever, like 40 km ish. This mod prevents that switch from happening, which I like. I prefer to stay in Free mode and I don\u0027t like the camera switching by itself.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"maja","CreatedById":168379,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-11-03T17:42:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong style=\u0022background-color:#f9f9f9;color:#2d3134;font-size:18px;\u0022\u003ENew release for KSP 1.12.2 is live!\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}